50 UTC\\n### 02:50 \u2014 RESUMING\\n\\n**Context:** New day detected (2026-04-14). No session memory found for the last 7 days.\\n**Last session summary:** N/A (First session for this agent/project context).\\n**Current state:** AI Factory foundation is established. Context library contains core manuals (Tier 1) and Design Archaeology (Tier 3) covering Skills implementation and Factory strategy. No active APP_BRIEF detected.\\n**Next:** Establish the project baseline or start the Architect Questionnaire.\\n\"}},\"text\":null}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"grounding_metadata\":null,\"partial\":null,\"turn_complete\":null,\"finish_reason\":null,\"error_code\":null,\"error_message\":null,\"interrupted\":null,\"custom_metadata\":null,\"usage_metadata\":null,\"live_session_resumption_update\":null,\"input_transcription\":null,\"output_transcription\":null,\"invocation_id\":\"e-d9f358f6-c8d0-4f50-a546-bf1f71b7047e\",\"author\":\"architect_agent\",\"actions\":{\"skip_summarization\":null,\"state_delta\":{},\"artifact_delta\":{},\"transfer_to_agent\":null,\"escalate\":null,\"requested_auth_configs\":{}},\"long_running_tool_ids\":null,\"branch\":null,\"id\":\"8d09d3fc-4988-421e-8f14-fa77d0683dfd\",\"timestamp\":1776154199.467537},{\"content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":\"CuoKAY89a18LwVH0DoTnxci7NYaWJF7HKOZt34o167ZfpRMxvfDnPH_8ExqvoJdN6afv3EiPX-2SnWwNoPz8yGvtye_sCJUt7GCVADFWk8rMBKgoGfA6AhmEjymwKmieZAVKfasBxk7yK6EsTV7YvNgTvVRHGxSE3GNIjwcPCskMFKIq6yu_TQBIIRWN9vV91HqwKmXHYw-EvBnOL-eOm230OJiXYXK5YcmrmaEScaVPWOyiiDk-kfCkVN8kx9lE9aaAVZFTCZt0T2FB2l79nS7r-ykLiTbXcldPx807rXUl6q2k66ivZ0l61ADRDQBEtYRK1GO_nBAupPSXnlLw7xFJgU8mypW7Xd9vUFYacz-QhV1nKyI1CMHScGMZx2Jqt5TGECzS7u2PiNAjBnYSNjGPZkjCIg_j5SPgu9roe5HRfKFvf0ZyUOZtCUBaWohSHD9QEs0mNxEJR91xyZJSEPXj4sNQtn_IoyXlANSqINPBJK4_Uye_gjCNurUWAB1dP2ehFcCwOD_Ytdca84RkZS-qQG6k4RQFV4da_unv3H3Pa7nk2IZmTFdm5BVj602zdncsVbcAl8xBsAk9opm9VRYkgVQZ-2p02YaQEgDpt0aOWUu0tLF_LJIbnX9